cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the problem of top-k document retrieval, which is a common task in information retrieval (IR) and database systems (DB). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes new algorithms and data structures, which suggests that it may belong to cs.DS (data structures) and cs.AI (artificial intelligence) sub-categories. Finally, the paper presents experimental results, which indicates that it may also belong to cs.LG (machine learning) sub-category.
